{"tid":2492391,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是好靚午 塔香松露台式燒雞(半隻) 牛油果沙律 漬物 椒鹽爆溪蝦 芥末秋葵","createTime":"2021-04-17T05:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T06:53:24.000Z","uid":33359,"like":45,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"03fd490731895c08f87906730aad2d1a32fc3326","tid":2492391,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmepyU2ToRVEMCdJeGKiaE3hKLLGiuPPNsNhfGNwLGdFdG?filename=CXsotX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXsotX4.jpg&h=9cb8281f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTCVSTvyz7MBB5vwEjWQC48cQ2p2SbQhg3wTpyED1rzS5?filename=ORDV4wq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORDV4wq.jpg&h=1d0bf35d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUBNLtuPEdCQxU2Sci5At4cQYqVHJ1HbwbbMtMV56poKU?filename=C8ofj4K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8ofj4K.jpg&h=16542c6e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYr81V7Yo1d93G9iza2C56896NRPDToEFMX9TJ3rHr7dQ?filename=Y1c0wbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1c0wbp.jpg&h=bbfae718&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間是第二次黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢加咗D新菜色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都係試返上次好想試既燒雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙律新鮮好味,由其係個D車厘茄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我懷疑係台灣既玉女番茄黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甜到好似食士多啤梨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三樣小菜同上次一樣唔多講,好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燒雞燒得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞皮好香脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最正係佢調味既比例好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為九層塔同松露都係濃味野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好容易喧賓奪主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢把握得幾好,一食落口先係雞香味,之後先慢慢滲出淡淡地既九層塔同松露味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢另外仲俾咗一細兜黑松露醬俾我點黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞肉就算係雞胸位都唔澀,好香雞油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同樣係燒雞,呢間對比我平時食個間係好味好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我食開個間性價比都高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然無收加一服務費<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但服務比好多有收加一既更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成間鋪既妹妹仔都有台妹FEEL<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個肚仔好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4db5cf3ce81b749417b4a8621749e0813212e4e","tid":2492391,"uid":39852,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"狗唔食得草<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56be35789ddbf9c82bb4aefab3c413aa9125bde6","tid":2492391,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b1886e231400a46b2aa7635d880dfd59c1e3f2","tid":2492391,"uid":128741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:33:32.000Z","msg":"台仔feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a866cb46b70dd067a5f910579b795ce6708752f0","tid":2492391,"uid":321789,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:33:49.000Z","msg":"<del>台妹</del>TB FEEL"},{"pid":"cacba35ddddbb000e3ed2697ef3a93d